Addressdata has seven-Parametters to run

addressdata <options> <address> 

Options:
-a  Add a address.
-i  Interactively. Allows you to add (-a) or remove (-r) an address interactively
-r  Remove address. Need an id of the given address, or the exact one.
-s  Search for address with the given parameters.
-c  Count addressdaten
-b  Show a banner
-bf Show a flower power banner.

Address:
Comma seperated values that are at least consists of 
name       :name of your family	 
surename   :your first name.
streetname :name of the street you're living in
housenumber:number of the house you're living in.
zip		   :your zip code.
city	   :village or city you're living in.
birthdate  :your birthday.	